data.description: Situated on 19 acres of picturesque land, this rural retreat combines modern eco-friendly features with rustic charm offering you the ultimate countryside lifestyle. Embrace a greener, more cost-efficient way of life with the state-of-the-art solar panel system. Enjoy reduced energy bills and a smaller carbon footprint while powering your oasis. Discover the joy of backyard farming with your very own chicken coop and 200 yard shooting range. Step into your own botanical paradise with the included greenhouse. Grow your own fresh produce or vibrant flowers all year round - thanks to this versatile addition to your property. The home features a BRAND NEW ROOF, BRAND NEW AC unit & heat pump both installed in 2023 as well as PAID OFF SOLAR PANELS! Get cozy by the fireplace! Filled with natural light and move-in ready, this property is a testament to pride of ownership. The Seller is also offering a $2500 buyer credit toward closing costs and $2000 carpet allowance with an acceptable offer!
